# Project Setup

## Project Structure

```sh
app/
├── components/           # Shared UI components
│   ├── ui/              # Shadcn UI components
│   └── features/        # Feature-specific components
├── lib/                 # Core utilities
│   ├── utils/          # Helper functions
│   ├── hooks/          # Custom hooks
│   └── types/          # Shared types
├── features/           # Feature modules
│   └── [feature]/
│       ├── api/        # Server functions & queries
│       │   ├── queries.ts    # TanStack Query hooks
│       │   └── mutations.ts  # TanStack Mutations
│       ├── components/ # Feature components
│       │   ├── index.ts      # Component exports
│       │   └── [Component]/  # Component files
│       ├── hooks/     # Feature hooks
│       │   └── index.ts      # Hook exports
│       ├── utils/     # Feature utilities
│       └── types/     # Feature-specific types
└── routes/             # Route components
    └── [feature]/      # Feature routes
```

## Technology Stack

### Core Technologies

- React 19 with automatic batching
- TypeScript with strict mode
- TanStack Router for type-safe routing
- TanStack Query for data fetching
- TanStack Form for form handling
- TanStack Start for server functions
- Drizzle ORM for database operations

### UI Layer

- Shadcn UI for components
- Tailwind CSS v4 for styling
- Radix UI for primitives

### Data Layer

- PostgreSQL for database
- Drizzle ORM for queries
- Zod for validation

## Project Initialization

### 1. Create Project

```bash
# Create new project
pnpm create tanstack-start my-app

# Install dependencies
cd my-app
pnpm install
```

### 2. Environment Setup

```bash
# Copy environment template
cp .env.example .env

# Generate environment types
pnpm env-types
```

### 3. Database Setup

```bash
# Create database
pnpm db:create

# Run migrations
pnpm db:migrate

# Generate types
pnpm db:types
```

## Configuration Files

### TypeScript Configuration

```typescript
// tsconfig.json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "target": "ES2022",
    "lib": ["DOM", "DOM.Iterable", "ES2022"],
    "module": "ESNext",
    "moduleResolution": "Bundler",
    "allowJs": true,
    "skipLibCheck": true,
    "strict": true,
    "noEmit": true,
    "esModuleInterop": true,
    "resolveJsonModule": true,
    "isolatedModules": true,
    "jsx": "preserve",
    "incremental": true,
    "baseUrl": ".",
    "paths": {
      "~/*": ["./app/*"]
    },
    "plugins": [
      {
        "name": "@tanstack/router-transformer"
      }
    ]
  },
  "include": ["**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx"],
  "exclude": ["node_modules"]
}
```

### ESLint Configuration

```javascript
// .eslintrc.js
module.exports = {
  extends: ['next', 'prettier', 'plugin:@typescript-eslint/recommended'],
  plugins: ['@typescript-eslint'],
  rules: {
    '@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars': ['error'],
    '@typescript-eslint/no-explicit-any': 'error',
    'react-hooks/rules-of-hooks': 'error',
    'react-hooks/exhaustive-deps': 'warn',
  },
};
```

### Prettier Configuration

```javascript
// .prettierrc.js
module.exports = {
  semi: true,
  trailingComma: 'all',
  singleQuote: true,
  printWidth: 80,
  tabWidth: 2,
};
```

## Development Scripts

```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "tanstack-start dev",
    "build": "tanstack-start build",
    "start": "tanstack-start start",
    "lint": "eslint . --ext .ts,.tsx",
    "format": "prettier --write \"**/*.{ts,tsx,md}\"",
    "typecheck": "tsc --noEmit",
    "db:migrate": "drizzle-kit push:pg",
    "db:types": "drizzle-kit generate:pg",
    "test": "vitest",
    "test:e2e": "playwright test"
  }
}
```

## Git Configuration

### Git Ignore

```gitignore
# Dependencies
node_modules
.pnpm-store

# Build
dist
.next
out

# Environment
.env
