!.env.example

# IDE
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea

# Testing
coverage
playwright-report

# Misc
.DS_Store
*.pem
```

### Git Hooks

```bash
#!/bin/sh
# .husky/pre-commit

pnpm lint-staged
```

```json
// package.json
{
  "lint-staged": {
